title: Fight Club
plot: An office worker suffering from insomnia meets a soap salesman, and together they form an underground fight club that spirals out of control.
tagline: First rule: You do not talk about Fight Club.

title: The Matrix
plot: A computer hacker named Neo discovers that his world is a simulated reality created by intelligent machines, and joins a rebellion to fight for humanity's freedom.

title: American Beauty
plot: A depressed suburban father in a mid-life crisis becomes infatuated with his teenage daughter's best friend, leading him to change his life in dramatic ways.

title: The Sixth Sense
plot: A troubled child psychologist begins treating a young boy who claims to see dead people, and uncovers a shocking truth about his own life.

title: The Green Mile
plot: A death row corrections officer witnesses supernatural events surrounding an inmate with mysterious healing powers, leading him to question justice and fate.

title: Toy Story 2
plot: When Woody is kidnapped by a greedy toy collector, Buzz Lightyear and the other toys embark on a daring rescue mission to save their friend.

title: Eyes Wide Shut
plot: After a shocking confession from his wife, a New York doctor embarks on a night-long odyssey through the city's seedy underworld, confronting his darkest desires.

title: Being John Malkovich
plot: A puppeteer discovers a hidden portal that allows him to enter the mind of actor John Malkovich, leading to a surreal and bizarre journey of self-discovery.
tagline: Ever wanted to be someone else?

title: The Blair Witch Project
plot: Three film students venture into the Maryland woods to document the local Blair Witch legend, only to find themselves lost and terrorized by an unseen presence.

title: All About My Mother
plot: A grieving woman embarks on a journey to find the father of her deceased son, encountering a series of complex and emotional challenges along the way.
tagline: A woman's journey of loss and discovery.

title: The Emperor and the Assassin
plot: The story of China's first emperor and his rise to power is told through a tale of love, betrayal, and political intrigue.

title: Not One Less
plot: A determined young substitute teacher in rural China goes to great lengths to keep her class intact when one of her students goes missing.

title: The Iron Giant
plot: A young boy befriends a giant robot from outer space, and together they must evade government agents who want to destroy the metal giant.

title: The King of Masks
plot: An aging street performer in 1930s China takes on a young apprentice, only to discover a secret that changes his life and challenges his traditions.
tagline: A story of honor and tradition.

title: Himalaya
plot: A young boy must lead his people on a perilous journey through the mountains to secure their future and honor his father’s legacy.

title: Rosetta
plot: A young woman struggles to find work and maintain her dignity in a harsh world that seems determined to keep her down.

title: Kikujiro
plot: A lonely boy sets out on a journey to find his mother, accompanied by an unlikely and irresponsible companion who learns valuable life lessons along the way.

title: Beau Travail
plot: A tale of jealousy and betrayal unfolds among French Foreign Legion soldiers stationed in East Africa, leading to an inevitable confrontation.

title: Peppermint Candy
plot: The tragic story of a man's life is told in reverse, revealing the events that shaped his descent into despair and ultimate demise.
